{
  "stem": "13079.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Ilse was an extraordinary woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a wife of Standartenfuhrer Koch, who was one of the commandants of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a woman who [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] was not well educated but she had gone through the public schools that were in Germany at that time and had married this man who was older than she was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she at that time when she was in Buchenwald was a rather attractive girl-- physically and I don't know about mentally.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was an eye catcher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she used to parade around in front of these prisoners with tight fitting clothes, and when anybody whistled or ogled, she took down their number and reported them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they were reported, they were subjected to pretty severe punishment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that punishment consisted of being laid across a tabletop and their backsides exposed, and they were given a terrific beating-- what they call a 25.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the prisoner had to sing out with each blow the number, beginning at one and going up to 25.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, a lot of these prisoners couldn't speak German, and it was impossible for them to count in German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But a lot of them got around to learning how to count from one to 25.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if they made a mistake in the count, they'd go back to one so that the prisoner got a lot more than 25.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, as a result of these beatings many of these prisoners were-- died as a result of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not only was it a shock, but it would be a shock to a man who was in good health.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But to these prisoners it was the difference between life and death.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
